jobDescription: A 20-year old passionate chemist who is determined to cure cancer
aboutText: I am Mary Jane, a 20 year old passionate chemist and Chemical Biologist who is determined to cure cancer. I specialize in Chemical Spectography and EMFs, and I am dedicated to furthering my knowledge and expanding my skillset. I am an avid hiker and skier, which has honed my ability to problem-solve and think critically in challenging conditions. My experience in the field of chemistry, combined with my outdoor hobbies, has given me the skills and knowledge necessary to make a difference in the world of biochemistry. I am excited to continue my work and hope to make a positive contribution to the scientific community.
